snippet.title: Wonhon: A Vengeful Spirit - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Add to wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1294340/Wonhon_A_Vengeful_Spirit

Wonhon: A Vengeful Spirit is a paranormal stealth action game where you play as a vengeful spirit of a girl who was killed during a bloody war. Now, she has returned from the dead and with supernatural powers, she is out to get revenge for her people and punish those who murdered her.

Release date: Q4 2020.

Follow us:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/wonhonthegame
IndieDB: https://www.indiedb.com/games/wonhon-a-vengeful-spirit

Chat with us on Discord channel: https://discord.gg/8Sama6w

Wonhon: A Vengeful Spirit by Busan Sanai Games
Publisher - Super.com
